node.text:
& @pierreandresenizergues for their continued focus to those in need on the streets of Los Angeles, we know it makes a difference. 

 Since 1998, @etnies has steadily donated to the homeless on Skid Row through the LA Mission.  Over more than two decades the brand has given more than 50,000 pairs of shoes to the Los Angeles homeless population.
For etnies CEO @pierreandresenizergues giving to the homeless is very personal.  As a skateboarder he has always spent a lot of time in the streets and for a time he was homeless himself. . 

#etniesPastPastPresentFUTURE

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by etnies Skateboarding in Eiffel Tower with @trevormcclung, @redbullskate, and @redbullfrance. May be an image of 1 person, standing, monument and outdoors.

node.text: It’s go time! Redbull Conquest practice in front of the Eiffel Tower, this is crazy! Let’s go @trevormcclung. #EtniesPastPresentFuture @redbullskate @redbullfrance

Aspire-Inspire: See @mattberger_ rise from small town skate park to competing in the Olympics and everything in between! 

Check our story and Swipe up to the @monsterenergy Youtube. 

#etniesskateboarding #etniesPastPresentFUTUTE

#etniesskateboarding

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by etnies Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @redbull, @nassimlachhab, @redbullskate, and @etnies. May be an image of text.

node.text:
We’ve partnered up with @redbull Conquest Paris on Aug 17-18, as the world’s skate elite (including @nassimlachhab & @trevormcclung ) go head to head showcasing their skills around seven of the most iconic Parisian skate spot replicas. 
All happening live at Place du Trocadéro in full view of the Eiffel Tower.

Live broadcast 
👉 RedBull.com/ParisConquest

#etniesskateboarding #etniesPastPresentFUTURE

node.text:
#thowback to 2018 for the #etniesALBUM premiere in Paris 🇫🇷. Etnies was born in Paris and we can’t get enough of the city.  Here’s @chrisjoslin_ @aidancampbell @trevormcclung & @nassimlachhab enjoying some of what Paris has to offer.

#etniesskateboarding #etniesPastPresentFUTURE
